  "contentHtml": "<h1>Do While</h1>\n<p>Loops through a block of code once guaranteed.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Then continues if the condition is true.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\r\n    $i = 1;\r\n    do {\r\n        echo $i;\r\n        $i++;\r\n    } while ($i &#x3C; 10);\r\n?></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Small alteration to prove it runs at least once.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\r\n    $i = 12;\r\n    do {\r\n        echo $i;\r\n        $i++;\r\n    } while ($i &#x3C; 10);\r\n?></span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>",
